Suzee Slater https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Suzee_Slater 0 Suzanne M. Slater, also credited as Suzee Slater, is an American former actress and model best known as Leslie Todd in the horror film Chopping Mall. She had several minor roles in movies and television in the late 1980s and early 1990s before abruptly leaving the acting industry.
